{"tid":1470783,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"龜殼好似甩皮咁","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:40:51.000Z","uid":103397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e62be9762ce016b4708579c7c35a5317801e26c0","tid":1470783,"uid":103397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"最近發現隻龜個殼唔知點解好似甩皮咁，係咪皮膚病？定係缺乏啲咩營養？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMapQXt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMapQXt.png&h=7004d61f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DALpQXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDALpQXw.png&h=e2afb211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時有開燈俾佢地曬，但佢地極少上個台曬燈，唔知會唔會關事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQGo6Ch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQGo6Ch.jpg&h=275e2342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物方面平時就係食呢款，係龜鋪老闆推介嘅<br />\n平時都好肯食，仲食得好開心（我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n零食嗰啲都冇餵過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KkVhrCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKkVhrCM.jpg&h=2c6f28f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfnfXKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfnfXKs.jpg&h=44dc67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPKBHeD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPKBHeD.gif&h=be9d175e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完啲屎都係青色嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaZVdmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaZVdmV.jpg&h=3458d242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位有養龜龜嘅巴絲，有冇人試過類似情況？可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733763ee899875b92b3405cd856db6a67898fdc4","tid":1470783,"uid":103397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5446fb0a24aea2fed3349af6fd930e0bf7ef85e0","tid":1470783,"uid":103397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aaa7af574577a75f5471ae0177712fdccfb2c02","tid":1470783,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"睇醫生"},{"pid":"6949034843066aa6d6726c031ce4d05cf9cba8c1","tid":1470783,"uid":74276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/F-lKvRMVBdYH0KKFeYuy6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FF-lKvRMVBdYH0KKFeYuy6Q&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=adc66d75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/F-lKvRMVBdYH0KKFeYuy6Q</a><br />\n龜群 可以入去問下"},{"pid":"13cb1f3c6aeebe4a948c582a31b1aa102a9fe0c7","tid":1470783,"uid":103397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6949034843066aa6d6726c031ce4d05cf9cba8c1","tid":1470783,"uid":74276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:29:00.000Z","msg